# Super key
 = super key

# Start terminal
 + Return 

# Kill focused window
 + c

# Rofi menu
 + d
 + t

# Exit menu on bottom right:
 + Shift + e

# Lock the system
 + l

# Reload the configuration file
 + Shift + c

# Restart i3 inplace (preserves your layout/session, can be used to upgrade i3)
 + Shift + r

# i3 keybinding list
 + F1

# Git cheatsheet
 + F2
# Ctrl-p cheatsheet
 + F3
# Cheat_sh cheatsheet
 + F4
#
# Honza snippets cheatsheet
 + F5


# Change window focus
 + j focus left
 + k focus right
 + u focus up
 + i focus down

# Move a focused window
 + Shift + j move left
 + Shift + k move right
 + Shift + u move up
 + Shift + i move down

# Split in horizontal orientation
 + v 

# Split in vertical orientation
 + h 

# Enter fullscreen 
 + f fullscreen toggle

# Change container layout (stacked, tabbed, toggle split)
 + s layout stacking
 + g layout tabbed
 + e layout toggle split

# Toggle tiling / floating
 + Shift + space floating toggle

# Change focus between tiling / floating windows
 + space focus mode_toggle

# Focus the parent container
 + a focus parent

# Open new empty workspace
 + Shift + n

# Resize mode
 + r mode "resize"
        
 + j shrink width 
 + k grow width 
 + u grow height 
 + i shrink height 

# Resize mode back to normal
 + Return 
 + Escape 
 + r mode "default"

# Applications shortcuts
 + n exec nemo 
 + m exec evolution 
 + w exec firefox
 + x exec musikcube 
 + Shift + t exec tor-browser-en

 + z exec zettlr
 + shift + g galculator
 + Shift + z calendar

 + Up exec vifm
 + Left exec youtube-viewer
 + Right exec calcurse
 + Down exec xpad

 + Shift + a audacity
 + Shift + Up geany
 + Shift + Left transmission-gtk
 + Shift + Right zeal
 + Shift + Down c calibre
 + Ctrl + m exec alsamixer

F12 exec "scrot ~/%Y-%m-%d-%T-screenshot.png" exec notify-send "Snapshot taken"


